Description: ATTalesExpressionCriterion
        ==========================
        
        Smart folder criterion that stores TALES Expressions.
        Especially useful when you want to use a smart folder
        as a view on any folder in your site with contextual
        based filter expressions.
        
        
        Andreas Gabriel <gabriel at hrz uni-marbug de> - http://www.uni-marburg.de/hrz
        
        
        
